This paper discusses the issues related to data warehousing and decision making, which falls under the category of database systems (cs.DB). The paper proposes an extension to the XML warehouse benchmark, which involves processing and analyzing complex hierarchies, indicating the relevance to information retrieval (cs.IR) and data structures (cs.DS). The paper also discusses the use of business intelligence tools, which involves artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG) techniques.
